beer.beer_description:
The colour of burnished copper, strong with a caramely sweetness.  A malt driven beer, lightly balanced with our 
own Goldings and Willamette fresh hop flowers.  The grain make up in this beer is a tightly kept secret.  
It has taken 7 years to prerfect and is a very special blend of English malts, some of which are 
dark roasted to impart the toffee and sweet flavours of this ale.
